Package environment

Class Homepage

  • java.lang.Object
    • environment.Homepage
  • public class Homepage
extends java.lang.Object
    The homepage of the application with access to every part of the program. This class builds the UI of the Homepage with the help of ModelFactory for elements of the model of settings.
    Author:
    Wolkenfarmer

    • Constructor Detail

      • Homepage

        public Homepage​(javafx.scene.Group root)
        Builds the homepage of the application. For the building of the buttons in the model in settings ModelFactory is used. Ultimately, the height of the content gets calculated and the scrollbar accordingly updated.
        Parameters:
        root - A group to attach it's layout parts to.
